<div style="width:0;height:0;clear:both"></div><dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1>志波海燕</h1>
<a class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" href="javascript:;" nslog-type="10003105" target="_blank" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
<a class="lemma-discussion cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-discussion-link" href="/planet/talk?lemmaId=1435849" nslog-type="90000102" target="_blank"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_discussion-solid"></em>讨论<span class="num">999</span></a>
</dd>
</dl><div class="promotion-declaration">
</div><div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">志波海燕，<a href="/item/%E4%B9%85%E4%BF%9D%E5%B8%A6%E4%BA%BA" target="_blank">久保带人</a>漫画《<a data-lemmaid="5460" href="/item/%E6%AD%BB%E7%A5%9E/5460" target="_blank">死神</a>》中的登场角色。个性豪放开朗，内心温柔可亲。代替体弱多病经常不在的<a data-lemmaid="238588" href="/item/%E6%B5%AE%E7%AB%B9/238588" target="_blank">浮竹</a>，让队员团结一致的<a data-lemmaid="9579850" href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F/9579850" target="_blank">十三番队</a>的前副队长，尸魂界原来的五大贵族之一<a data-lemmaid="2040850" href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%B6/2040850" target="_blank">志波家</a>（已没落）的当家家主。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":1," data-sup="1">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_79464"> </a>
</div><div class="para" label-module="para">后在蓝染的阴谋中，为了救被<a data-lemmaid="1893680" href="/item/%E8%99%9A/1893680" target="_blank">虚</a>吞噬的妻子，为了一个男人的尊严而在与虚作战中被吞噬，为了不拖累同伴而自愿撞上<a data-lemmaid="942419" href="/item/%E6%9C%BD%E6%9C%A8%E9%9C%B2%E7%90%AA%E4%BA%9A/942419" target="_blank">朽木露琪亚</a>的刀尖最后牺牲<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":2," data-sup="2">
[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_79464"> </a>
。</div>
</div>
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-focusAndRelation">
