<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="角色形象"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>角色形象</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_1_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="身份背景"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="1-1"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>身份背景</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/0/58ee3d6d55fbb2fb05a49da54f4a20a44723dcfe?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:165px;" target="_blank" title="">
<img alt="" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/-fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=0c220684738da9774a2f81298050f872/58ee3d6d55fbb2fb05a49da54f4a20a44723dcfe.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
</div><b></b>出身于<a href="/item/%E5%B0%B8%E9%AD%82%E7%95%8C" target="_blank">尸魂界</a>贵族<a href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F" target="_blank">志波家族</a>，毕业于尸魂界<a href="/item/%E7%9C%9F%E5%A4%AE%E7%81%B5%E6%9C%AF%E9%99%A2" target="_blank">真央灵术院</a>，修行地在西<a href="/item/%E6%B5%81%E9%AD%82%E8%A1%97" target="_blank">流魂街</a>三地区北端鲤伏山。为尸魂界<a href="/item/%E6%8A%A4%E5%BB%B7%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">护廷十三队</a>中<a href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">十三番队</a>前副队长，上级是身体病弱但善良温和的<a href="/item/%E6%B5%AE%E7%AB%B9%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E9%83%8E" target="_blank">浮竹十四郎</a>队长<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":3," data-sup="3">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_79464"> </a>
。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_1_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="相貌衣着"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="1-2"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>相貌衣着</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/0/e865a69990a483366f068c41?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:165px;" target="_blank" title="海燕与露琪亚初期见面">
<img alt="海燕与露琪亚初期见面" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=94cb12fa51da81cb4ae684cf6267d0a4/f703738da97739128abe7f6ff8198618367ae220.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
海燕与露琪亚初期见面
</span>
</div>黑色头发、深烟青瞳孔，左手腕有<a href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E5%AE%B6" target="_blank">志波家</a>的家纹“崩裂的堕天涡潮”刺青。有志波家标志性的长长下睫毛。鼻梁上有天生的印记。发尾微长。发型相貌有些类似黑发的一护<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":3," data-sup="3">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_79464"> </a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="1_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_1_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="性格特点"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="1-3"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>性格特点</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">够仁义又讲义气，是受到很多队员敬慕的有人望的好男人。不管身份立场如何，海燕都能够无差别的对待同队的每一位队士。他公正的态度，不管是贵族出身的队士还是流魂街出身的队士都很喜欢他。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":1," data-sup="1">
[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_79464"> </a>
对妻子温柔关切，对队长非常尊敬和体贴辅佐，对部下们有着朋友般的热忱和大哥般的照顾，在朽木露琪亚加入<a href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">十三番队</a>后，亲自教导她各种战斗方式，对其格外关怀<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":3," data-sup="3">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_79464"> </a>
。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">作者在附录特典集赋予海燕的关键词为“阳”。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":4," data-sup="4">
[4]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[4]_79464"> </a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="角色能力"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>角色能力</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="2" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<table class="transparentBorder" log-set-param="table_view" width="99%"><tr><td align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para"><b><a href="/item/%E6%96%A9%E9%AD%84%E5%88%80" target="_blank">斩魄刀</a></b>：<a href="/item/%E6%8D%A9%E8%8A%B1" target="_blank">捩花</a></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">日语：ねじばな</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">英语：Nejibana<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":5," data-sup="5">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_79464"> </a>
</div>
</td><td align="center" valign="middle" width="100"><div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/0/43a7d933c895d143ca0b506b70f082025aaf077c?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:205px;" target="_blank" title="捩花">
<img alt="捩花" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=b68826feca177f3e1434fb0f40ce3bb9/43a7d933c895d143ca0b506b70f082025aaf077c.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:205px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
捩花
</span>
</div></div>
</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="top"><div class="para" label-module="para">解放语：水天逆卷け，捩花！（让水天逆卷吧，捩花！）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">属性：水系</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">解放形态：<a href="/item/%E6%96%A9%E9%AD%84%E5%88%80" target="_blank">斩魄刀</a>成为如海皇波塞冬一般的三叉戟型长枪，末端为螺旋形锥状。游戏中为水蓝色缨，动画及漫画彩图中为深蓝。有旋、刺、挑等枪术，伴随着周围产生波涛般的灵子水花，看起来像是劈波斩浪的招式一般。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">攻击方式：使用独特的高架势，以单手腕为轴心，用回转作为主要攻击，是舞蹈般的枪术，然后利用伴随着枪击一同卷起的波涛，将敌人压碎并两断。（露琪亚语）<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":6,:7," data-sup="6-7">
[6-7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[6-7]_79464"> </a>
</div>
</td><td align="center" valign="middle" width="100"><div class="para" label-module="para"><a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/16116543/c995d143ad4bd1131a4c037a59afa40f4afb05f0?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover" nslog-type="10000206" style="width:222px;" target="_blank" title="始解">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:209px;">
<img alt="始解" class="picture" src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=a0abfe466409c93d03f209f5af3cf8bb/c995d143ad4bd1131a4c037a59afa40f4afb05f0.jpg" style="width:220px;height:209px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
始解<span class="number">(4张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:214px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:208px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="人际关系"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>人际关系</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div>
<table class="table-view log-set-param" log-set-param="table_view" width="658"><tr><th width="42">关系</th><th width="74">姓名</th><th width="541">介绍</th></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>妻子</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74">志波美亚子</td><td valign="top" width="541">或译<a href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E9%83%BD" target="_blank">志波都</a>，已故，与海燕同在<a href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">十三番队</a>，为第三席，由于她的牺牲导致海燕为了尊严与梅塔史塔西亚战斗而死<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":5," data-sup="5">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_79464"> </a>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top"><b>下属</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top"><a href="/item/%E6%9C%BD%E6%9C%A8%E9%9C%B2%E7%90%AA%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">朽木露琪亚</a></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top">与海燕同为十三番队队员，颇受海燕照顾，海燕牺牲于露琪亚的斩魄刀上<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":8," data-sup="8">
[8]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[8]_79464"> </a>
</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>妹妹</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74">志波空<a href="/item/%E9%B9%A4" target="_blank">鹤</a></td><td valign="top" width="541"><div class="para" label-module="para">因哥哥死于死神之手而对声称死神十分厌恶，实际上已从浮竹十四郎那里了解真相<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":9," data-sup="9">
[9]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[9]_79464"> </a>
</div>
</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>弟弟</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74"><a href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E5%B2%A9%E9%B9%AB" target="_blank">志波岩鹫</a></td><td valign="top" width="541">因哥哥死于死神之手而自称为西边流魂街最讨厌死神的人<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":10," data-sup="10">
[10]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[10]_79464"> </a>
</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>家仆</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74"><a href="/item/%E9%87%91%E5%BD%A6" target="_blank">金彦</a>、<a href="/item/%E9%93%B6%E5%BD%A6" target="_blank">银彦</a></td><td valign="top" width="541">原来是监督教育海燕和空鹤的，在志波家衰败的时候只有他们一直留下来照看志波家</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>宠物</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74">波尼</td><td valign="top" width="541">野猪，后成为岩鹫的坐骑</td></tr><tr><td valign="top" width="42"><b>伯父</b></td><td colspan="1" rowspan="1" valign="top" width="74"><a href="/item/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83" target="_blank">黑崎一心</a></td><td valign="top" width="541"><div class="para" label-module="para">同是志波家族的人，是海燕的长辈<a href="/item/11" target="_blank"><sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":11," data-sup="11">
[11]</sup></a><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[11]_79464"> </a>
</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="角色经历"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>角色经历</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="4_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_4_1"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="早期经历"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="4-1"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>早期经历</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/203128/d048addea6e58914ccbf1a90?fr=lemma&amp;ct=cover" nslog-type="10000206" style="width:222px;" target="_blank" title="志波海燕剧情截图">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:220px;height:165px;">
<img alt="志波海燕剧情截图" class="picture" src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=fc3b48745343fbf2c12ca121807fca1e/fcfaaf51f3deb48fb633cca2f01f3a292df57877.jpg" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
志波海燕剧情截图<span class="number">(20张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:214px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:208px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
海燕是名天才，他在进入死神统学院“<a href="/item/%E7%9C%9F%E5%A4%AE%E7%81%B5%E6%9C%AF%E9%99%A2" target="_blank">真央灵术院</a>”的考试中一次合格，成功进入灵术院学习，当时的灵力已经达到六等。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">只用了一年就修行完了六年的课程，成为三席进入<a href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">十三番队</a>。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">之后只用了五年便担任了护庭十三队十三番队的副队长。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">由于队长<a href="/item/%E6%B5%AE%E7%AB%B9%E5%8D%81%E5%9B%9B%E9%83%8E" target="_blank">浮竹十四郎</a>身体病弱，所以平时由海燕代替他全权管理队务<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":3," data-sup="3">
[3]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[3]_79464"> </a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="4_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_4_2"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="战死沙场"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="4-2"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>战死沙场</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">因为妻子被<a data-lemmaid="1299250" href="/item/%E8%93%9D%E6%9F%93%E6%83%A3%E5%8F%B3%E4%BB%8B/1299250" target="_blank">蓝染惣右介</a>制造的实验体，有融合能力的虚——<a href="/item/%E6%A2%85%E5%A1%94%E5%8F%B2%E5%A1%94%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">梅塔史塔西亚</a>吞噬而死去，为了替妻子报仇，海燕与梅塔史塔西亚展开激烈战斗，却不料该<a data-lemmaid="1893680" href="/item/%E8%99%9A/1893680" target="_blank">虚</a>的能力是让<a href="/item/%E6%96%A9%E9%AD%84%E5%88%80" target="_blank">斩魄刀</a>消失，海燕不幸被能力特殊的梅塔史塔西亚吞噬<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":5," data-sup="5">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_79464"> </a>
，为了维护理智和尊严，海燕自愿撞上露琪亚的斩魄刀而牺牲。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":2," data-sup="2">
[2]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[2]_79464"> </a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">他的逝去给露琪亚留下了无尽的思念、悔恨、遗憾和无法开解的苦痛<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":8," data-sup="8">
[8]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[8]_79464"> </a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="4_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_4_3"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="灵体被夺"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="4-3"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>灵体被夺</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">志波海燕被有融合能力的<a href="/item/%E6%A2%85%E5%A1%94%E5%8F%B2%E5%A1%94%E8%A5%BF%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">梅塔史塔西亚</a>吞噬，梅塔史塔西亚被<a href="/item/%E6%9C%BD%E6%9C%A8%E9%9C%B2%E7%90%AA%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">朽木露琪亚</a>所斩杀之后，和被其融合的志波海燕的灵体一起被返送<a href="/item/%E8%99%9A%E5%9C%88" target="_blank">虚圈</a>重新构造。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":12," data-sup="12">
[12]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[12]_79464"> </a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/0/d56b36349eeb960f5bb5f582?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:165px;" target="_blank" title="亚罗尼洛·艾鲁鲁耶利">
<img alt="亚罗尼洛·艾鲁鲁耶利" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=9c0a4f804aed2e73f8e9812eb700a16d/08f790529822720ea68342fe7bcb0a46f21fab61.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
亚罗尼洛·艾鲁鲁耶利
</span>
</div>第九<a href="/item/%E5%8D%81%E5%88%83" target="_blank">十刃</a><a href="/item/%E4%BA%9A%E7%BD%97%E5%B0%BC%E6%B4%9B%C2%B7%E8%89%BE%E9%B2%81%E9%B2%81%E8%80%B6%E5%88%A9" target="_blank">亚罗尼洛·艾鲁鲁耶利</a>吞噬了死亡的梅塔史塔西亚后，因此拥有了梅塔史塔西亚的无限融合进化能力，并获了志波海燕的灵体和记忆，可以变身为志波海燕的相貌。海燕自身的意识思想已经死去，构成灵体和记忆的灵力被亚罗尼洛的“<a href="/item/%E5%99%AC%E8%99%9A" target="_blank">噬虚</a>”能力所融合，成为其自身的灵力。亚罗尼洛只是获取了海燕的相貌、能力和记忆中的经验，与真实的志波海燕并无生命和意识上的延续关系，因此不能单纯理解为“就是同一人”。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":13," data-sup="13">
[13]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[13]_79464"> </a>
已被露琪亚用叄舞·白刃击败。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":14," data-sup="14">
[14]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[14]_79464"> </a>
露琪亚在<a href="/item/%E8%99%9A%E5%9C%88" target="_blank">虚圈</a>一战中，不得不克服心理阴影与其战斗。<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":15,:16," data-sup="15-16">
[15-16]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[15-16]_79464"> </a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="4_4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_4_4"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="死后影响"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="4-4"></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">志波海燕</span>死后影响</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" href="/pic/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E6%B5%B7%E7%87%95/1435849/0/0b07ec1fdfbaa45df724e457?fr=lemma&amp;ct=single" nslog-type="9317" style="width:220px;height:165px;" target="_blank" title="海燕与露琪亚聊天">
<img alt="海燕与露琪亚聊天" class="lazy-img" data-src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=221a4d18cffc1e17f9bf8b337a91f67c/f603918fa0ec08fa308ee9a959ee3d6d55fbda36.jpg" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="width:220px;height:165px;"/>
</a>
<span class="description">
海燕与露琪亚聊天
</span>
</div>海燕曾经是<a href="/item/%E6%9C%BD%E6%9C%A8%E9%9C%B2%E7%90%AA%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">朽木露琪亚</a>崇拜的对象，而且因为与<a href="/item/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%E4%B8%80%E6%8A%A4" target="_blank">黑崎一护</a>的相似使在他身上的谜团也越来越多，在被<a href="/item/%E5%B0%B8%E9%AD%82%E7%95%8C" target="_blank">尸魂界</a>得知<a href="/item/%E9%9C%B2%E7%90%AA%E4%BA%9A" target="_blank">露琪亚</a>的死神之力被人类（黑崎一护）拿走后，特地派<a href="/item/%E5%85%AD%E7%95%AA%E9%98%9F" target="_blank">六番队</a>队长<a href="/item/%E6%9C%BD%E6%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%93%89" target="_blank">朽木白哉</a>（露琪亚的大哥）与六番队副队长<a href="/item/%E9%98%BF%E6%95%A3%E4%BA%95%E6%81%8B%E6%AC%A1" target="_blank">阿散井恋次</a>（露琪亚的青梅竹马）来到现世将露琪亚强行带回尸魂界，在一护被朽木白哉刺中倒地后，朽木白哉对要跑到倒地满身是血的一护身边的露琪亚说过“其实这个小鬼（指一护）跟他（指海燕）非常的像”，如此而来海燕应该是故事发展的关键人物之一。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">529话说明<a href="/item/%E9%BB%91%E5%B4%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83" target="_blank">黑崎一心</a>原名志波一心，是<a href="/item/%E5%BF%97%E6%B3%A2%E7%A9%BA%E9%B9%A4" target="_blank">志波空鹤</a>的伯父，海燕应该是一护的堂哥，所以长得像也可以理解了<sup class="sup--normal" data-ctrmap=":11," data-sup="11">
[11]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[11]_79464"> </a>
。</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a class="lemma-anchor para-title" name="5"></a>
<a class="lemma-anchor" name="sub79464_5"></a>
